## Backend changes

- `*.controller.ts` or `*.service.ts` changed → `/api-contract`
- `schema.prisma` changed → `/db-migrate` before migrating
- New Prisma field → `/prisma-field` (updates schema + admin.service.ts + wiki)
- New module `src/modules/<name>/` → `/new-system`
- `*.middleware.ts` / `*.guard.ts` → record in wiki/Architecture/
- `*.dto.ts` changed → check class-validator annotations

### For vibe-coders
- DO NOT put Prisma queries in controllers — use services
- DO NOT store secrets in code — all in .env
- Always validate via DTOs (class-validator)
- Rate limits on every public endpoint
- Logging via Nest Logger, not console.log
